task.summary: Added exclude params to Wordpress API
Fixed SharedPreferences can't return Integer as String
Updated Facebook Audience SDK and added Facebook Native Ads delegate
Added NativeAdView.Type to Configuration & changed some method names
Added max. ads displayed & init default
Clear endless scroll state on refreshing data
Used NativeAdsManager to load set of ads
Update ads module & added Const variables
Added Spotlight fields in data module
Applied Spotlight with SpotlightVM & model fields
Config to show Spotlight and CategorySelect or not
Fixed bug related to WpArticle model not having id
Added External URL support for Contentful
Implemented Realm for Add Tab feature
